Widespread Service Degradation**:\n   - Multiple services (shipping, product catalog) show significant latency increases\n   - The pattern suggests a systemic issue rather than an isolated service failure\n\nThe root cause appears to be related to the cart service and its Redis dependency, which are showing the most severe performance degradation. The checkout process is being significantly impacted as a result.", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对故障期间指标数据的全面扫描，我发现了多个显著的异常指标和潜在问题。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存资源严重不足，node_memory_usage_rate从35.26%飙升到52.45%，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes减少27.8%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 35.26→52.45 (+48.8%), node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 10.4GB→7.5GB (-27.8%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间异常，rrt_max从4834ms增加到7268ms，p99响应时间增长147%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 4834ms→7268ms (+40.2%), p99: 12169ms→80113ms (+147%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"错误率显著上升，client_error_ratio的p99值从0.29增加到0.71\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio p99: 0.29→0.71 (+83.9%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"错误率异常，error_ratio的p99值从0.17增加到0.41\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio p99: 0.17→0.41 (+82.0%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点CPU使用率上升，node_cpu_usage_rate从25.68%增加到27.63%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_cpu_usage_rate: 25.68%→27.63% (+7.3%), p99: 29.27%→40.49% (+32.2%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现：\n\n1. **节点级资源问题**：aiops-k8s-05节点内存使用率显著上升（+48.8%），可用内存大幅减少，这可能影响该节点上运行的pod性能。\n\n2. **服务性能异常**：多个服务出现响应时间增长和错误率上升：\n